title: Anneke van Giersbergen leaving The Gathering
author: christian
content: <p><a href="http://www.omroepbrabant.nl/news.aspx?id=83197">Sad news</a> this morning in my feed reader; Anneke van Giersbergen, singer of <a href="http://www.gathering.nl/">The Gathering</a> is leaving the band after 13 years for starting a new band called <a href="http://www.aguadeannique.com/">Agua de Annique</a>.</p> 	<ul> 	<li><a href="http://www.gathering.nl/news.php?id=857">Band&#8217;s statement</a></li> 	<li><a href="http://blog.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=blog.view&#38;friendID=80545931&#38;blogID=272698767&#38;MyToken=896c7dc1-3716-4215-b7a2-b3cf592307a2">Anneke&#8217;s statement</a></li> 	</ul> 	<p>I hope they will both find their ways and come back at both their full strengths, then we will have <em>two</em> great acts.</p>
